---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /essays/
title: Essays
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<section class="essays-index">

  <header class="essays-index__header">
    <p class="essays-index__eyebrow">Essays</p>
    <h1>Threads through the archive</h1>
    <p class="essays-index__lede">
      The pages of these scrapbooks are best read in their own running order,
      but several threads of family history cross multiple volumes and
      decades. These essays trace those threads — pulling together the
      sources that document each one and putting them in historical context.
    </p>
  </header>

  <ol class="essays-list">
    {%- for essay in collections.essay | sortByOrder -%}
      <li class="essays-list__item">
        <a href="{{ essay.url }}">
          <h2 class="essays-list__title">{{ essay.data.title }}</h2>
          {% if essay.data.summary %}
            <p class="essays-list__summary">{{ essay.data.summary }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </a>
      </li>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </ol>

</section>
